StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProspectProfessedExam]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ProspectId uniqueidentifier
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ProspectProfessedExamId, ProspectId, ProspectProfessedExamType, Score1, Score2, Score3, ExamDate, ExamEnteredDate, LastUpdateUserId FROM [USMC].ProspectProfessedExam
WHERE ProspectId = @ProspectId
END
